![121.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1586301601168-IFI4FUEV5ID5MMOWP7AQ/121.jpg)

What would the Justice League do if an unstoppable techno-organic virus was tearing its way through the DC Universe? Writer Tom Taylor hopes to answer that question with his critically acclaimed Elseworlds story **DCeased!** Comic and horror fans rejoice as we are treated to a tension-filled tale of epic proportions, as our heroes deal with a virus that makes people want to claw their faces off. When it is revealed that the virus doesn't discriminate, the story becomes a race against time for the survival of all humanity!  
   
If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](/comicbookclique/episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
